<h1 class="m-0">Timeline</h1>

<p>
  <a href="https://antonbobrov.github.io/vevet/classes/Timeline.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Docs</a>
  /
  <a href="https://github.com/antonbobrov/vevet-demo/blob/main/src/pages/timeline/index.ts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Source Code</a>
</p>

<p class="lead">A basic timeline. It does not support DOM animation etc. Use for simple custom animations.</p>

<hr class="my-4" />

<div class="d-flex flex-row justify-content-start align-items-center gap-1">
  <button id="play" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Play</button>

  <button id="pause" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Pause</button>

  <button id="reverse" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Reverse</button>

  <button id="reset" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Reset</button>
</div>

<input
  class="my-4"
  id="range"
  type="range"
  min="0"
  max="1"
  value="0"
  step="0.0001"
  style="width: 100%;"
/>

<div class="my-2" style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 20px; background-color: #dedede;">
  <div
    id="thumb"
    style="position: absolute; top: -5px; left: 0; width: 10px; height: 30px; transform: translate(-50%, 0); background-color: #000;"
  ></div>
</div>

